descriptionHtml:
This is my first mod of many to come so please download this and tell me if you liked it, it there were any bugs, or any suggestions as i will be checking this quite often.

Requirements: Skyrim
NO DLC REQUIRED

The house is just a door (sorry i will update that but for now it will be a door) and it is located in Whiterun behind the Breezehome.

You enter a doorframe and you end up in a Medium-Large house.

PLease leave anything you can to make this mod better because it is not that good. Like I said before this is my first mod!

4.5 hours or work put into this.
